model
Class Document

java.lang.Object
  model.Document

public class Document
extends java.lang.Object

Represents a document returned by RESTful search.

The result of a search request is a response document that is encoded in the format specified by the request parameter format.

Each result record contained in the response document is associated with a set of metadata fields. Each field has a name, and may be single-valued or multiple-valued.

Author:
Karem Terry
